          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "سَأَلَ أَحْمَدُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ أَبِي نَصْرٍ اَلرِّضَا عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ :"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " عَنِ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "اَلرَّجُلِ يَتَزَوَّجُ اَلْمَرْأَةَ مُتْعَةً أَ يَحِلُّ لَهُ أَنْ يَتَزَوَّجَ اِبْنَتَهَا بَتَاتاً"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " قَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:44:22",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/44/22",
      "text": [
        " \"لاَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4604 - Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Abi Nasr asked al-Ridha (as) about a man who marries a woman in Mut'ah (temporary marriage).\nIs it permissible for him to marry her daughter permanently?\nImam (as) replied: \"No.\""
        ]
      }
    },
